data.description: Serenity and Adventure Await! Gorgeous 5-Acre Discover the perfect blend of tranquility and excitement with this remarkable 5-acre property nestled amidst nature's embrace. This extraordinary estate presents a delightful home featuring 2 baths, 3 bedrooms, and the potential for a 4th bedroom  walk-out basement. The moment you arrive, you'll be captivated by the enchanting surroundings. Majestic trees paint the landscape, offering a sense of seclusion and privacy that is truly priceless. The hilly terrain adds character to the property, offering stunning vistas and boundless opportunities for exploration and adventure. The home has endless the possibilities. While it may need updates throughout, it offers the perfect canvas!
